description:
-Lists several main categories. For example TV, Movies, Tickets, Celebs etc..
-Under each main category, lists many subcategories 
-Easy to search and many interesting topics and subtopics

elements.name: Get the list of the top 250 movies

steps.name: that I am at the IMDB homepage
I have clicked on the menu button
I have clicked on top rated movies
I should be taken to the page with the list of top rated movies

elements.name: Sort top 250 movies list by number of ratings

steps.name: that I am on the top rated movies page
I select sort by number of ratings in the sort by box
the list should resort by number of ratings
